title: Tracings And Blueprints, ca. 1830
description: ceiling and side walls of la petite singerie at chantilly; 26 tracings and blueprints of ceiling decoration, 23 of side walls' decoration - bottom of framing panels number: 1, 2, 7, 11, 14, 16, and 17 missing, in tracing and blueprint

tombstone.epitaph: Tracings And Blueprints, ca. 1830.gelatine and paper. 1923-2-2-a/o.
